# Generated media stays out of git EXCEPT the README/npm demo, which has to be in the repo for the
# embed to resolve (npm renders the GIF; GitHub plays the mp4 from a raw URL). Regenerate with
# `npm run demo` — and remember each rebuild is a new binary blob in history, so don't re-commit it
# for cosmetic tweaks.
*.gif
*.mp4
*.mov
*.webm
!docs/demo.gif
!docs/demo.mp4
*.log
